postcontent: Up today is an amazingly accurate, reliable, compact, and all around fun weapon: the C39 AK pistol. This gun is awesome. Aside from being the first 100% American made AK, it features a fully milled receiver with an engraved US flag on the side. This has the "shark fin" front sight and a rear sight that is adjustable for both elevation AND windage. It also comes with a birdcage flash hider. title: For Sale:  Intratec Tec-22 Replacement Parts Pack  10 Pieces
location: Northwest Indiana   Lake County   Dyer, Indiana, United States
postcontent:
Our replacement parts pack consisting of 2 ea firing pin and firing pin rebound spring, 1- main spring, 1-High-Energy recoil spring, 1- hammer and the 3 piece "Ever Sharp" extractor assembly. The firing pins break frequently. And the rebound spring is lost or bent and is no longer useable. The braking problem is the result of "SHEAR" stress caused by the original design of the bolt. We could not change the design of the bolt's so we tried to help by trying new materials for the firing pins. We've made pin's from various kinds of steel including hardened A2 tool steel with little success. We tried heat treated the pin's to different hardness's. That didn't work either! We've even made a batch of firing pin's from Titanium. Much to our surprise, that batch broke even faster than the steel firing pins. Titanium is strong but it doesn't hold up well to "shear" stress.To insure that the firearms works as designed the main spring should be changed every year or two. The recoil spring is made of hi-test piano wire as are the main spring and firing pin rebound spring. We have been "Intratec Parts" since 1998. We aren't just order takers. When you buy from us you are getting our Intratec knowledge. We know the Intratec firearms inside and out. We know the little tricks that will help you replace the firing pin and spring as well as the main spring. When you have a problem with your Intratec firearm ask us...we will be able to help you.
